    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 8pt;}\n.html-preview .ConsPlusNonformat {font-family: 'Courier New'; font-size: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Фуқаролик ишлари бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Ариза берилган фуқаролик суди номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\"> судига</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Даъвогар: </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Даъвогарнинг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Даъвогарнинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Телефон: </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Даъвогарнинг телефон рақами</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Электрон почта манзили: </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Даъвогарнинг электрон манзили</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Жавобгар: </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Жавобгарнинг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> да яшовчи</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Жавобгарнинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Телефон: </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Жавобгарнинг телефон рақами</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Электрон почта манзили: </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Жавобгарнинг электрон манзили</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Даъво мазмуни:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold;\">ДАЪВО АРИЗА</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: italic;\">(алимент миқдорини камайтириш ҳақида)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">Мен ва жавобгар ўртамиздаги <span class=\"leading\"></span>қонуний никоҳ </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#15}Никоҳ қайд қилинган ФҲДЁ органи номи </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#16}Никоҳ қайд қилинган вақт</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\"> куни </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#17}Никоҳни қайд этиш далолатномаси рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">-сон билан қайд этилган.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">Биргаликдаги турмушимиздан </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#18}Боланинг туғилган вақти </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">да туғилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#19}Боланинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\"> исмли (туғилганлик ҳақида гувоҳнома серияси </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#20}Болага берилган туғилганлик тўғрисидаги гувоҳнома рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#21}Болага гувоҳнома берган ФҲДЁ органи номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\"> томонидан берилган) фарзанд (фарзандларим)им бор. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">Фуқаролик ишлари бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#22}Алимент ундиришга оид суд ҳужжати чиққарган суд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\"> туманлараро судининг </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#23}Алимент ундиришга оид суд ҳужжати чиққан сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\"> даги (суд буйруғи, ҳал қилув қарори)га асосан жавобгардан вояга етмаган </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#18}Боланинг туғилган вақти </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\"> да туғилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#19}Боланинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\"> исмли фарзанд (фарзандлар)имни моддий таъминоти учун алимент ундириш белгиланган. <span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\"> Бугунги кунда </span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#24}Алимент миқдорини камайтиришга асослар баён этилади</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">Жавобгар билан ўртамизда фарзандимиз (фарзандларимиз)ни моддий таъминоти ҳақида келишув мавжуд эмас.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">Юқоридагиларга кўра, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Оила Кодексининг 105-моддасига асосан </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold;\">СЎРАЙМАН:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"structures structure-25\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#25}Жавобгарнинг туғилган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">да туғилган жавобгар </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#11}Жавобгарнинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\"> фойдасига </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#18}Боланинг туғилган вақти </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">да туғилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#19}Боланинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\"> исмли фарзандим (фарзандларим)нинг моддий таъминоти учун фуқаролик ишлари бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#22}Алимент ундиришга оид суд ҳужжати чиққарган суд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\"> туманлараро судининг </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">{#23}Алимент ундиришга оид суд ҳужжати чиққан сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">даги <span class=\"leading\"></span>(суд буйруғи, ҳал қилув қарори)га асосан мендан ундирилиши белгиланган</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">алимент миқдорини камайтиришни. </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">(22) Илова қилинаётган ҳужжатлар</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">– даъво ариза нусхаси</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">– давлат божи тўланганлигини тасдиқловчи хужжат.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">– суд буйруғи нусхаси</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">– алимент миқдорини камайтиришга асос қилиб келтирилган ҳолатларни тасдиқловчи хужжатлар нусхаси.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">– ишончнома нусхаси </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: italic;\">(даъво ариза ишончли вакил томонидан берилган тақдирда)</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt;\">.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Даъвогар </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#6}Даъвогарнинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\"> </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 377.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#3}Ариза берилган сана</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
